prefix = Ctrl+a  or  Ctrl+Space

── Sessions ──
prefix + :new          New session
prefix + s             List sessions
prefix + $             Rename session
prefix + d             Detach
prefix + (             Previous session
prefix + )             Next session
prefix + L             Last active session

── Windows (tabs) ──
prefix + c             New window (same path)
prefix + ,             Rename window
prefix + w             List windows
prefix + n             Next window
prefix + p             Previous window
prefix + l             Last active window
prefix + 1-9           Go to window by number
prefix + .             Move window to another index
prefix + &             Close window

── Panes (splits) ──
prefix + \             Split horizontal
prefix + -             Split vertical
prefix + h/j/k/l      Resize pane (vim keys, repeatable)
prefix + m             Maximize/restore pane
prefix + z             Zoom/unzoom pane (fullscreen)
prefix + !             Break pane into new window
prefix + :join-pane -t :N   Move pane to window N
prefix + o             Cycle to next pane
prefix + ;             Last active pane
prefix + x             Close pane
prefix + q             Show pane numbers
prefix + {             Move pane left
prefix + }             Move pane right
prefix + Space         Cycle pane layouts (flip h↔v)
prefix + M-1           Layout: even-horizontal
prefix + M-2           Layout: even-vertical
prefix + E             Equalize pane sizes
prefix + X             Pane manager (kill/jump processes)

── Copy / Scroll ──
Trackpad               Scroll directly
prefix + [             Enter copy/scroll mode
Ctrl+s                 Search forward (in copy mode)
Ctrl+r                 Search backward (in copy mode)
prefix + ]             Paste buffer
q                      Exit copy mode

── Other ──
prefix + a             Agent dashboard (Claude Code monitor)
prefix + g             Lazygit popup (current dir)
prefix + T             Terminal popup (current dir)
prefix + i             Info popup (dir + git summary)
prefix + /             Search keybindings (this menu)
prefix + r             Reload config
prefix + :             tmux command line
prefix + ?             Full keybinding list (raw)
prefix + t             Show clock
